":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hgjddzM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhgjddzM.png&h=c956aa71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0bWbmu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0bWbmu.png&h=ac1ae4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OoZpkeR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOoZpkeR.png&h=1613dfe3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcfbe6bc662c54fb1ca5df0af7e5f5247089dd01","tid":2133082,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:20:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Andy26473514/status/1288805011149881346?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndy26473514%2Fstatus%2F1288805011149881346%3Fs%3D20&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=26dafc71\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAndy26473514%2Fstatus%2F1288805011149881346%3Fs%3D20&h=09972001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Andy26473514/status/1288805011149881346?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"154ae732ec746d83f37e851ccb7700169cfd8c7c","tid":2133082,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T23:21:36.000Z","msg":"20200729納瓦羅先生分別連線GMA以及CNN為羥氯喹站台！2/2<br />\n（CNN部分）<br />\n1.納瓦羅先生反覆強調這是65年的老藥，在醫生的監督下不會傷害身體<br />\n2.納瓦羅先生讀過超過60篇論文，裡面的證據證明羥氯喹在早期有壓倒性效果<br />\n3.納瓦羅先生：如果最後我是對的，那麼成千上萬的美國人就將死於媒體和FDA妖魔化羥氯喹"},{"pid":"9d85ae82953e0d74f0869d2e89968e6b5d6b6d71","tid":2133082,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T00:35:10.000Z","msg":"羟氯喹抗冠狀病毒三大原理<br />\n<br />\n1.滲透並鹼化胞內體(Endosome)和溶酶體(lysosome)，阻斷或減慢病毒入侵路徑(2016)<br />\n2.將鋅元素帶入細胞，抑制RNA複製酶，阻止病毒複製自身的RNA基因代碼(2010,2014)<br />\n3.與ACE-2受體旁的某分子結合，從而阻止病毒與ACE-2受體結合而入侵細胞內(2020)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/llyzs/status/1288852034674806784?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fllyzs%2Fstatus%2F1288852034674806784%3Fs%3D20&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=b7d69e7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fllyzs%2Fstatus%2F1288852034674806784%3Fs%3D20&h=6d119f08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/llyzs/status/1288852034674806784?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"24f42f17cd6045aba8be111eff600bb84632338c","tid":2133082,"uid":90987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991e76d933d857c4cead4718bd6b386c8922d175","tid":2133082,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T19:26:08.000Z","msg":"印度開始大量用緊"},{"pid":"6054c27857499a38fa0012653e380060a5dd12b3","tid":2133082,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b38730d43416056f4792da551f7add4602f3308c","tid":2133082,"uid":349653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX483zeApsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGX483zeApsM&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=e5094fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX483zeApsM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閆麗夢話支田共高層知道HCQ可以預防covid-19？<br />\n<br />\n不過有副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅唔堅？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T19:36:22.000Z","msg":"trump四月個時食黎預防，<br />\n之後比人屌話冇科學根據，<br />\ntrump應該都收到風先會食，<br />\n唔會係咁啱食同一隻。"},{"pid":"9ce5601d5151232be04e23673e13208d89ebdc5c","tid":2133082,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T20:07:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4e76261b67dbb1bd85869b1b2cb757b6edf191","tid":2133082,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T00:08:50.000Z","msg":"臨床試過無乜用"},{"pid":"8fb6f677553028fc7589f298986ea5861912e715","tid":2133082,"uid":90987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6054c27857499a38fa0012653e380060a5dd12b3","tid":2133082,"uid":33904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b38730d43416056f4792da551f7add4602f3308c","tid":2133082,"uid":349653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T20:55:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX483zeApsM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGX483zeApsM&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=e5094fcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GX483zeApsM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n閆麗夢話支田共高層知道HCQ可以預防covid-19？<br />\n<br />\n不過有副作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅唔堅？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T19:36:22.000Z","msg":"trump四月個時食黎預防，<br />\n之後比人屌話冇科學根據，<br />\ntrump應該都收到風先會食，<br />\n唔會係咁啱食同一隻。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\n咁啱果吓先鬼<br />\n另外fb ig 大舉delete 緊一條片係外國醫生公開話hcq有用"},{"pid":"1d416755bb7a34262d36f681210e9040888380b1","tid":2133082,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c4e76261b67dbb1bd85869b1b2cb757b6edf191","tid":2133082,"uid":204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T00:08:50.000Z","msg":"臨床試過無乜用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:44:00.000Z","msg":"Link?"},{"pid":"3644c38a3207312c25ff5085255ac1cef8fd96f2","tid":2133082,"uid":78295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 我會信閰麗夢同trump都唔會信WHO<br />\n<br />\n等睇人抹黑HCQ"},{"pid":"41bca6311ceac55bb82d55c48dc6fdf444a05c2e","tid":2133082,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"呢隻藥係alternative fact 撚最愛"},{"pid":"a5534f53b969ff02e93685029493d8884f8c1029","tid":2133082,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3644c38a3207312c25ff5085255ac1cef8fd96f2","tid":2133082,"uid":78295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 我會信閰麗夢同trump都唔會信WHO<br />\n<br />\n等睇人抹黑HCQ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"你當我抹黑, 事實你要自己判斷<br />\n<br />\n1 絕大數據係in vitro. Clinical 係無差別<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2019014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2019014&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=cd806cd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2019014</a><br />\n當然仲有大把反例, small sample size paper, 所以叫controversial<br />\n<br />\n2 FDA 羅列副作用. 評估風險覺得自己唔死得既可以拎自己做白老鼠<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/nda/2020/OSE%20Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%20-%2019May2020_Redacted.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessdata.fda.gov%2Fdrugsatfda_docs%2Fnda%2F2020%2FOSE%2520Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%2520-%252019May2020_Redacted.pdf&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=36ed788c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/nda/2020/OSE%20Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%20-%2019May2020_Redacted.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3 三個antiviral 機制 (in vitro)<br />\n- 改變lysosomal pH 等病毒無法響細胞內釋放<br />\n- as Zinc ionophore引Zn 離子入cell 抑制 病毒RNA複製<br />\n- HCQ黐住ACE2 receptor鄰近既sialic acid 等阻住病毒同ACE2 結合<br />\n<br />\n以上三個同醫瘧疾機制唔同<br />\n<br />\n4 輕症有醫生用HCQ配合Zinc治療<br />\n<br />\n5 有人話HCQ係approved drugs. 但係咪醫武漢肺炎就有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有人話愛滋都可以食藥嚟降低感染, 但人哋係有clinical data. HCQ 既數據相信仲build up緊. 如果閣下想試都得但可惜你既成效唔會俾人記低<br />\n<br />\n個人結論: 姑勿論佢有無效都好, 現階段我唔會將食HCQ當預防性治療. 至緊要係避免接觸傳染同戴口罩做好個人衛生. 萬一HCQ係對輕症有效(重症會踩多腳造成心肌損害幫埋武漢肺炎整死個病人)至少個supply仲響度. 當然人係自私, 但要食就要日日食唔係都無效. 當個supply runs out, 想預防既同等緊治療想一試既就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無事, 做足個人衛生既想唔想未有疫苗之前都日日食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己諗清諗楚喇"},{"pid":"9df20e52b45c895af6fadc8640e0b145ee86a2dc","tid":2133082,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老老豆豆 我會信閰麗夢同trump都唔會信WHO<br />\n<br />\n等睇人抹黑HCQ</blockquote>你當我抹黑, 事實你要自己判斷<br />\n<br />\n1 絕大數據係in vitro. Clinical 係無差別<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2019014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nejm.org%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1056%2FNEJMoa2019014&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=cd806cd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nejm.org/doi/full/10.1056/NEJMoa2019014</a><br />\n當然仲有大把反例, small sample size paper, 所以叫controversial<br />\n<br />\n2 FDA 羅列副作用. 評估風險覺得自己唔死得既可以拎自己做白老鼠<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/nda/2020/OSE%20Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%20-%2019May2020_Redacted.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accessdata.fda.gov%2Fdrugsatfda_docs%2Fnda%2F2020%2FOSE%2520Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%2520-%252019May2020_Redacted.pdf&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG16%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=36ed788c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.accessdata.fda.gov/drugsatfda_docs/nda/2020/OSE%20Review_Hydroxychloroquine-Cholorquine%20-%2019May2020_Redacted.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n3 三個antiviral 機制 (in vitro)<br />\n- 改變lysosomal pH 等病毒無法響細胞內釋放<br />\n- as Zinc ionophore引Zn 離子入cell 抑制 病毒RNA複製<br />\n- HCQ黐住ACE2 receptor鄰近既sialic acid 等阻住病毒同ACE2 結合<br />\n<br />\n以上三個同醫瘧疾機制唔同<br />\n<br />\n4 輕症有醫生用HCQ配合Zinc治療<br />\n<br />\n5 有人話HCQ係approved drugs. 但係咪醫武漢肺炎就有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonde